  "keyFeatures": [
    "3500+ guided quests covering all aspects of mod progression",
    "GregTech-centered technology tree with EU power system and tiered machinery",
    "Balanced tech and magic integration (Thaumcraft, Blood Magic, Botania, Witchery)",
    "Realistic ore vein generation requiring multi-dimensional mining",
    "Over 200 mod integrations refined over 10+ years of active development",
    "Custom world generation with Realistic World Gen and Biomes O' Plenty",
    "Space progression via Galacticraft and Galaxy Space for endgame resources",
    "Active multiplayer community with official and community-run servers"
